com.fluffy_minions.prototype.needsCalculators

Class TotalNeedsCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fluffy_minions.prototype.needsCalculators.TotalNeedsCalculator

  • public class TotalNeedsCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores and computes all the necessary ingredients a person needs in a day.
